henever you're back in range.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="7bb974ca-4f91-47fc-8c0e-afcd6ab28881" class="r-d46rte" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="d6b413f1-9285-425c-a46c-a5144cb51c93" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1clur2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1s1kkr3"><div data-rid="d01a2884-875d-4d64-ab73-1ba917bcc487" class="r-1ox33ot alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How accurate is the shot tracking?</p></span></div><div data-rid="bfbfd5fd-4d1f-4cf4-9412-6444fea0bdd2" class="r-zkpi5p" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-66l86i" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R1clur2:"><div data-rid="51947c49-ac5e-41f8-aca4-b7392048ccdb" class="r-ayx1fd"><div data-rid="e18c4cf0-8d9f-4954-9f55-6823f5bc82d8" class="r-9ags1g alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Arccos Air detects shots with a high degree of accuracy from your very first round — and it gets better as you play. The AI is trained on 1.5 billion+ real golf shots from golfers at every level and trusted by PGA TOUR professionals. If a shot is occasionally missed or added, minor edits in the app take seconds and give you insights you can trust.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="d6866e9d-e577-494c-a005-435b63014cdd" class="r-1biczf8" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="cbb04d6c-a6ce-4819-bc12-c607cfa1f241" class="r-1yjhuga" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="c8fb31e0-0e37-4a36-bf6c-134a3745514d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rdlur2:" tabind